InventoryItems.Name: wood chopping set
InventoryItems.Description: The Campfire Kids Wood Chopping Set brings the great outdoors ... indoors. Young lumberjacks can test their mettle splitting this reusable break-apart log. Take the axe and give it a swing to chop the log in half, and then snap it back together for more log splittin' fun. The easy chopping action makes it safe and easy to use. Ages 3 and up.
